{"tid":1708991,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"長遠被罷工之新方法","createTime":"2019-11-11T19:03:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T22:54:47.000Z","uid":259648,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"f2d2744ff741744773d8554d647850da86110573","tid":1708991,"uid":259648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T19:03:17.000Z","msg":"［干擾八達通］<br />\n八達通係大部分人搭車畀錢嘅方法。<br />\n<br />\n八達通使用 13.56 MHz 頻率連接。<br />\n我嘅諗法係用阻隔相應頻率嘅物料（如：金屬紙）貼喺八達通讀卡器上，從而令讀卡器感應唔到八達通。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.octopus.com.hk/en/document/interference-shield-guide.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.octopus.com.hk%2Fen%2Fdocument%2Finterference-shield-guide.pdf&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=ff0f0bc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.octopus.com.hk/en/document/interference-shield-guide.pdf</a><br />\n以八達通公司嘅防干擾卡為例，將佢反轉貼喺讀卡器上，應該可以阻隔讀卡器/八達通嘅頻率。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tcqVifO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtcqVifO.png&h=b50beb21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n防干擾卡應該要有拍卡機圖案，而且大小相同，底嗰面有強力膠。拍卡入閘時就神不知鬼不覺貼上去，從而令人返工時用八達通拍卡入唔到閘。黨鐵，巴士，小巴都貼得。<br />\n<br />\n不過要時間準備物資，而且要用nfc測試，因為唔知work唔work。<br />\n以上純屬個人諗法～唔知巴打絲打有咩意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fbb9f5d9529e3c1eab68ec241124d4a702c43c1","tid":1708991,"uid":254630,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T19:03:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191112/RRQC6TB7M6YFEDTOSF2PK2QTJE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191112%2FRRQC6TB7M6YFEDTOSF2PK2QTJE%2F&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQezNZxTp5Qnzjcs1Ew7Eoms%3D&h=8fe17f9b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20191112%2FRRQC6TB7M6YFEDTOSF2PK2QTJE%2F&h=30fded17\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20191112/RRQC6TB7M6YFEDTOSF2PK2QTJE/</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20191112/large/1573491126_5caf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20191112%2Flarge%2F1573491126_5caf.jpg&h=7f926344&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b977687d5f18dd0ed2186b3f9081c024b0ae2229","tid":1708991,"uid":259648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T19:07:11.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"8d72f7b70a3dcdb72dd7533f69ce91f635faeb07","tid":1708991,"uid":259648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T19:08:30.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"2b672b0fc01282381d160f2f94764aa6b1078b89","tid":1708991,"uid":314909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T19:58:56.000Z","msg":"今朝啲港豬直接跳閘"},{"pid":"b36c3ef81be80628b0377d469c29fb26a20e0843","tid":1708991,"uid":287329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T22:54:47.000Z","msg":"推你<br />\n雖然我唔識"}]}